locality: Région de l'Anosy. Bemangidy Forest, ca. 3 km E of Antsotso, along RN 12a, 65 km N of Ft. Dauphin. Remnant humid forest along creeks just below forest edge. Plants treated in alcohol before drying. Collected with J. Rabenantoandro, F. Randriatafika, E. Lowry, E. Ramisy & B. Mara.
